ğŸ“Œ 5. Flow Components

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ”¹ Agents

Perform tasks.

ğŸ”¹ Tasks

Define what must be done.

ğŸ”¹ Process Type

Defines execution logic:

* Sequential
* Hierarchical

ğŸ”¹ Shared Memory

Passes context between tasks.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ“Œ 6. How Data Flows Between Agents

```text
Agent A Output
   â†“
Stored in Shared Memory
   â†“
Agent B Reads Output
   â†“
Builds Next Step
```

This ensures:

* Context continuity
* Reduced hallucination
* Logical progression

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ“Œ 7. CrewAI Flow vs LangGraph

| Feature           | CrewAI Flow        | LangGraph             |
| ----------------- | ------------------ | --------------------- |
| Structure         | Role-based         | Graph-based           |
| Looping           | Limited            | Advanced              |
| Dynamic Branching | Basic              | Powerful              |
| Best For          | Role collaboration | Complex orchestration |

